- malloc hooks were deprecated in recent versions of glibc
- regression tests for all recent fixes
- regression test for killing process
- lmdbg-grep: -f <n> output n first stacktraces
- lmdbg-grep: -l <n> output n last stacktraces
- lmdbg-sym: option to NOT generate source.c:NN or funcname component
- lmdbg-leaks: native order of leaks, earlier allocated -- earlier in output
- lmdbg-leaks written in C (libJudy)
- lmdbg-leaks: double free
